tion",{"title":80,"path":81,"stem":82},"queryCollectionItemSurroundings","/docs/utils/query-collection-item-surroundings","docs/4.utils/3.query-collection-item-surroundings",{"title":84,"path":85,"stem":86},"queryCollectionSearchSections","/docs/utils/query-collection-search-sections","docs/4.utils/4.query-collection-search-sections",{"title":88,"icon":89,"path":90,"stem":91,"children":92,"page":42},"组件","i-lucide-square-code","/docs/components","docs/5.components",[93,97,101],{"title":94,"path":95,"stem":96},"内容渲染器","/docs/components/content-renderer","docs/5.components/0.content-renderer",{"title":98,"path":99,"stem":100},"插槽","/docs/components/slot","docs/5.components/1.slot",{"title":102,"path":103,"stem":104},"文章组件","/docs/components/prose","docs/5.components/2.prose",{"title":106,"icon":107,"path":108,"stem":109,"children":110,"page":42},"部署","i-lucide-cloud-upload","/docs/deploy","docs/6.deploy",[111,115,119,123,127,131,135,139,143],{"title":112,"path":113,"stem":114},"服务器","/docs/deploy/server","docs/6.deploy/1.server",{"title":116,"path":117,"stem":118},"无服务器","/docs/deploy/serverless","docs/6.deploy/2.serverless",{"title":120,"path":121,"stem":122},"NuxtHub","/docs/deploy/nuxthub","docs/6.deploy/3.nuxthub",{"title":124,"path":125,"stem":126},"Cloudflare Pages","/docs/deploy/cloudflare-pages","docs/6.deploy/4.cloudflare-pages",{"title":128,"path":129,"stem":130},"Vercel","/docs/deploy/vercel","docs/6.deploy/5.vercel",{"title":132,"path":133,"stem":134},"Netlify","/docs/deploy/netlify","docs/6.deploy/6.netlify",{"title":136,"path":137,"stem":138},"AWS Amplify","/docs/deploy/aws-amplify","docs/6.deploy/7.aws-amplify",{"title":140,"path":141,"stem":142},"Docker","/docs/deploy/docker","docs/6.deploy/8.docker",{"title":144,"path":145,"stem":146},"静态","/docs/deploy/static","docs/6.deploy/9.static",{"title":148,"icon":149,"path":150,"stem":151,"children":152,"page":42},"高级用法","i-lucide-code-xml","/docs/advanced","docs/7.advanced",[153,157,161,165,169,173,177,181],{"title":154,"path":155,"stem":156},"全文搜索","/docs/advanced/fulltext-search","docs/7.advanced/1.fulltext-search",{"title":158,"path":159,"stem":160},"原始内容","/docs/advanced/raw-content","docs/7.advanced/2.raw-content",{"title":162,"path":163,"stem":164},"SQL 存储","/docs/advanced/database","docs/7.advanced/3.database",{"title":166,"path":167,"stem":168},"调试工具","/docs/advanced/tools","docs/7.advanced/4.tools",{"title":170,"path":171,"stem":172},"钩子","/docs/advanced/hooks","docs/7.advanced/5.hooks",{"title":174,"path":175,"stem":176},"自定义来源","/docs/advanced/custom-source","docs/7.advanced/6.custom-source",{"title":178,"path":179,"stem":180},"LLM 集成","/docs/advanced/llms","docs/7.advanced/7.llms",{"title":182,"path":183,"stem":184},"转换器","/docs/advanced/transformers","docs/7.advanced/8.transformers",{"title":186,"icon":187,"path":188,"stem":189,"children":190,"page":42},"Nuxt Studio","i-lucide-monitor","/docs/studio","docs/8.studio",[191,195,199,203,207,211],{"title":192,"path":193,"stem":194},"设置","/docs/studio/setup","docs/8.studio/1.setup",{"title":196,"path":197,"stem":198},"同步","/docs/studio/github","docs/8.studio/2.github",{"title":200,"path":201,"stem":202},"内容编辑器","/docs/studio/content","docs/8.studio/3.content",{"title":204,"path":205,"stem":206},"媒体库","/docs/studio/medias","docs/8.studio/4.medias",{"title":208,"path":209,"stem":210},"应用配置","/docs/studio/config","docs/8.studio/5.config",{"title":212,"path":213,"stem":214},"本地调试","/docs/studio/debug","docs/8.studio/6.debug",{"page":216,"surround":286},{"id":217,"title":218,"body":219,"description":279,"extension":280,"links":281,"meta":282,"navigation":283,"path":163,"seo":284,"stem":164,"__hash__":285},"docs/docs/7.advanced/3.database.md","数据库",{"type":220,"value":221,"toc":271},"minimark",[222,226,242,245,249,252,255,258,261,265,268],[223,224,225],"p",{},"在 Content v3 中，我们引入了基于 SQLite 的强大存储层，提供了一种强大且高效的内容管理方法。这相比之前基于文件的存储系统是一个显著的提升，后者在性能和可扩展性方面存在局限。",[227,228,229,232],"blockquote",{},[223,230,231],{},"在 Content v2 中，系统在 Nitro 运行时读取并解析内容，为每个内容文件创建缓存文件以存储解析数据。这种方法给网站运行时带来了相当大的开销。",[233,234,235,239],"ul",{},[236,237,238],"li",{},"生产环境中的 I/O 时间较长，因为模块必须加载所有缓存文件来搜索内容。",[236,240,241],{},"此外，由于内容缺乏优化和压缩，导致包体积较大，特别在边缘环境中表现尤为明显。",[223,243,244],{},"Content v3 的内容管理包含三个关键步骤，旨在简化流程并提升性能。",[246,247,248],"h2",{"id":248},"生成数据库转储文件",[223,250,251],{},"对于项目中的每个集合，模块从定义的源读取内容并解析成抽象语法树（AST）。基于集合的模式为每个集合创建特定的表。然后将解析后的内容插入对应的表中，确保数据结构与定义的模式一致，以实现最佳查询效果。所有内容最终保存到转储文件中。",[246,253,254],{"id":254},"冷启动时还原转储文件",[223,256,257],{},"在运行时，当应用执行首次内容查询时，模块会读取前一步生成的转储文件，并将其还原到目标数据库中。该过程快速且针对不同部署模式和平台进行了优化。",[223,259,260],{},"模块采用了特殊的完整性检查机制，确保数据库内容更新到最新状态。该完整性检查机制还能防止重复导入，保持数据存储的完整性和准确性。",[246,262,264],{"id":263},"浏览器中的-wasm-sqlite","浏览器中的 WASM SQLite",[223,266,267],{},"针对客户端导航，模块采用类似的方法。当应用执行首次内容查询时，会从服务器下载生成的转储文件，并在浏览器中初始化本地 SQLite 数据库。从此之后，所有查询均在本地执行，无需调用服务器，大大提升了应用响应速度并提供无缝用户体验。",[223,269,270],{},"这一架构不仅提升了性能，还支持离线功能，使用户即使在无网络连接时也能访问内容。服务器端与客户端的结合确保 Nuxt Content v3 功能强大且灵活，适用于广泛的用例和环境。",{"title":272,"searchDepth":273,"depth":273,"links":274},"",4,[275,277,278],{"id":248,"depth":276,"text":248},2,{"id":254,"depth":276,"text":254},{"id":263,"depth":276,"text":264},"Nuxt Content 如何存储和检索内容","md",null,{},{"title":162},{"title":218,"description":279},"yyIQgUehHGyxyBicrXBIFX1sxfNJvrHf-tvjVDtAy48",[287,289],{"title":158,"path":159,"stem":160,"description":288,"children":-1},"访问应用中的内容原始数据",{"title":166,"path":167,"stem":168,"description":166,"children":-1},{"data":291,"body":292},{},{"type":293,"children":294},"root",[295],{"type":296,"tag":223,"props":297,"children":298},"element",{},[299],{"type":300,"value":279},"text",1749797812521]